profile:
Spring cleaning has a new sense of urgency this year, with the advice of the US center of disease and control, now more than ever people are washing, dusting and disinfecting their homes and workplaces and now have an increased need for a good deep clean. 

Now more than ever cleaners are taking every precaution while deep cleaning. From wearing gloves, shoe covers and masks to disinfecting vacuums between appointments and using hand sanitizer frequently. 

A deep clean means finding all the little spots, adding hours to a traditional cleaning, this is where we clean over and under every surface giving your home the Ultimate Clean! It doesn't stop there, the cleaning is only half the job. The CDC recommends spraying surfaces with a household bleach or a household cleaner with at least 70% alcohol. This will kill those germs that can cause viral respiratory illness. 

So with a deep clean and a disinfectant your home will be sparkling by the time we're finished!

We are a complete cleaning and detailing service team providing cleaning services to BOTH Residential and COMMERCIAL PROPERTIES. 

Our goal is to enhance your business or home by making it feel brand new every single time we clean it. The owners have a combined experience of 30 years in the cleaning industry. Whether your lifestyle is consumed with work and/or family, life demands of today are much more hectic in comparison to years ago. Our mission is to have our clients walk in the door and breathe a sigh of relief. Just knowing that our  job was well done so that they can enjoy their day and evening. Stand out above the rest when you choose our team to clean your office or home.

All of our employees go through extensive police checks before being hired onto our company, we pride ourselves in our friendly and professional staff.

We ARE changing the way people see clean and raising the Bar for industry standards
